{1. Character Name:Goya}
{2. Race (e.g., dragonborn/gnome/half-elf/half-orc/tiefling/kobold/bugbear):Human Male}
{3. Class (e.g., Rogue/Warlock/Wizard/Druid/Bard/Cleric/Gunslinger):Rogue}

Next, let us delve into my character's personality and beliefs. Answer these queries to unveil my alignment, and backstory.

